        ''' -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
        ''' <summary>
        ''' LoadSettings loads the settings from the Database and displays them
        ''' </summary>
        ''' <remarks>
        ''' </remarks>
        ''' <history>
        ''' 	[cnurse]	11/11/2004  created
        ''' </history>
